 2015-08302015-06-17,  AAFC,  FPCC,  ,  , 
ActFarm Products Agencies Act
SubjectProclamation Amending the Canadian Beef Cattle Research, Market Development and Promotion Agency Proclamation
PrecisOrder directing that a PROCLAMATION do issue AMENDING THE CANADIAN BEEF CATTLE RESEARCH, MARKET DEVELOPMENT AND PROMOTION AGENCY PROCLAMATION which will allow the development of a new organizational structure that will maximize the efficiency and effectiveness of domestic and international beef marketing activities and provide for additional funds generated through simplified administration and the elimination of duplication.
